Cap. Ribavirin 200 mg. : US$ 6.90/Pack of 4 capsules.
Syrup Ribavirin 50mg./5ml : US$ 2.75/30ml Bottles.
The above is correct and accurate as it was represented to me by the
exporter in India."
Again, oral ribavirin.
The ADFL army is closing in on Kinshasa and may overrun it before very long.
Who knows where those soldiers have been? Will US and other UN forces be
deployed on the ground in Zaire? In Kinshasa, to protect embassies and their
staffs and other expatriates?
The last thing any of us would like to see are congressional hearings as to
